DESCRIPTION:
The freedom of The Sims 3 inspires its unpredictability and offers endless opportunities for fun and games! Create millions of unique characters and control their lives. Modify their appearance and character. Build houses for them, from luxury villas to exclusive furniture to quaint cottages. Submit their heroes explore the ever-changing world of open beyond the threshold of his house and get acquainted with other characters. Download the exclusive content and share their work with other players on the network. The new system of fast goals and rewards allows you to decide the fate of the heroes of The Sims 3, and execute (or break!) Their dreams and plans.
Created the character of their dreams and put it unique traits of character! Adjust the appearance and character of the characters on the taste. Which character do you create: a hopeless romantic, an evil genius or a paranoid kleptomaniac? The fate of the characters in your hands! Fulfill the dreams of your players, performing (or not performing) their desires. Will your heroes nimble thieves, rock stars and world leaders - it depends only on you.
Changes all around! Build the home of your dreams characters. Before you open the unlimited customization of their clothes, furniture or vehicles. Explore the new area! Send characters to meet friends in the park, on a date at a diner, a visit to the neighbors or even chat with a not very attractive inhabitants of cemeteries.

